  <h2 id="frontend">Frontend Development</h2>
  <p>
    Frontend development focuses on the user interface - everything visible in the browser.
  </p>

  <h3>Core Technologies</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>HTML:</strong> The skeleton - defines structure and content</li>
    <li><strong>CSS:</strong> The skin - controls appearance and layout</li>
    <li><strong>JavaScript:</strong> The muscles - adds interactivity and dynamic behavior</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Modern Frontend Development</h3>
  <pre><code>{`<!-- Modern HTML5 structure -->
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>My Web App</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav><!-- Navigation --></nav>
    </header>
    <main>
        <article><!-- Content --></article>
    </main>
    <script src="app.js"></script>
</body>
</html>`}</code></pre>

