  <ul>
    <li><strong>React:</strong> Component-based library by Facebook (most popular)</li>
    <li><strong>Vue.js:</strong> Progressive framework, easy to learn</li>
    <li><strong>Angular:</strong> Full-featured framework by Google</li>
    <li><strong>Svelte:</strong> Compiler-based approach, minimal runtime</li>
  </ul>

