    <li><strong>Vercel:</strong> Great for frontend frameworks (Next.js, Astro)</li>
    <li><strong>Netlify:</strong> Easy static site and serverless deployment</li>
    <li><strong>Railway/Render:</strong> Full-stack app hosting</li>
    <li><strong>AWS/Azure/GCP:</strong> Enterprise cloud platforms</li>
  </ul>

